/*
 * 
 * in hibernate, we can select product in 4 ways
 * 
 * -> by Id
 * -> by HQL
 * -> by Criteria API
 * -> by Native SQL
 * 
 * 
 * ----------------------------------------------------------------
 * 
 * 
 * advantages of HQL
 * ---------------------
 * 
 * 
 * -> OO query lang
 * -> DBMS independent
 * 
 * 
 * 
 */

